e3[0].List5[0].Lia[0].Checkbox5cb[0]\",\n    \"description\": \"Item 5a - Filing where defendant lives\",\n    \"page\": 3,\n    \"value\": \"/1\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"field_id\": \"SC-100[0].Page3[0].List6[0].item6[0].ZipCode1[0]\",\n    \"description\": \"Item 6 - Zip code where defendant lives\",\n    \"page\": 3,\n    \"value\": \"94086\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"field_id\": \"SC-100[0].Page3[0].List7[0].item7[0].Checkbox60[1]\",\n    \"description\": \"Item 7 - No, not attorney-client dispute\",\n    \"page\": 3,\n    \"value\": \"/2\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"field_id\": \"SC-100[0].P"]
