[402.772496, "o", "Plaintiff (list names):\r\n\r\nCase Number:\r\n\r\nJoyce He\r\n3\r\n\r\nb. When did this happen? (Date): 2025-09-30\r\nIf no specific date, give the time period: Date started: 2026-01-19\r\n\r\nThrough:\r\n\r\nc. How did you calculate the money owed to you? (Do not include court costs or fees for service.)\r\nI have asked the defendant to return the money multiple times via text but he is not responding. The amount is\r\nlisted on the signed roommate sublease contract.\r\n\r\nCheck here if you need more space. Attach one sheet of paper or form MC-031 and write “SC-100, Item 3” at\r\nthe top.\r\n4\r\n\r\nYou must ask the defendant (in person, in writing, or by phone) to pay you before you\r\nsue. If your claim is for possession of property, you must ask the defendant to give you\r\nthe property. Have you done this?\r\n✖\r\n\r\n"]
[402.772629, "o", "5\r\n\r\nYes\r\n\r\nNo\r\n\r\nIf no, explain why not:\r\n\r\nWhy are you filing your claim at this courthouse?\r\nThis courthouse covers the area (check the one that applies):\r\na.\r\n\r\n✖\r\n\r\nb.\r\n"]
