[431.694135, "o", "The \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K (the person, business, or public entity being sued) is:\r\nName: Zhi Chen\r\n\r\nPhone: 5125658878\r\n\r\nStreet address: 299 W Washington Ave\r\nStreet\r\n\r\nSunnyvale\r\n\r\nCA\r\n\r\n94086\r\n\r\nCity\r\n\r\nState\r\n\r\nZip\r\n\r\nCity\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[K--\u001b[m\u001b[K\r\nIf the \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K is a corporation, limited liability company, or public entity, list the person\r\nor agent authorized for service of process here:\r\nName:\r\n\r\nJob title, if known:\r\n\r\nAddress:\r\nStreet\r\n\r\nCity\r\n\r\nState\r\n\r\nZip\r\n\r\nCheck here if your case is against more than one \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K and attach form SC-100A.\r\nCheck here if any \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K is on active military duty and write \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K’s name here:\r\n3"]
[431.694275, "o", "\r\n\r\nThe plaintiff claims the \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K owes $ $1,500.00\r\n\r\n. (Explain below and on next page.)\r\n\r\na. Why does the \u001b[01;31m\u001b[Kdefendant\u001b[m\u001b[K owe the plaintiff money?\r\nDefendant failed to return my security deposit based on the signed roommate sublease contract after moving out.\r\n\r\nRev. January 1, 2026\r\n\r\nPlaintiff’s Claim and ORDER to Go to Small Claims Court\r\n\r\nSC-100, Page 2 of 6\r\n\r\n"]
